<title>MEXICO: RESEARCH ALERT-Televisa upgraded to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Televisa upgraded to buy.</headline>
<dateline>MEXICO CITY 1997-04-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>J.P. Morgan Securities Inc. said on Wednesday has upgraded Mexican media group Televisa to buy from long-term buy.</p>
<p>-- Analyst Matthew J. Harrington said in a research report the ADR was considerably oversold at Tuesday's closing price of 22-5/8.</p>
<p>-- &quot;There is 25 percent upside off our 1998 valuation, even if the potential for the Sky direct to home service is completely disregarded,&quot; Harrigton wrote.</p>
